snippet.title: Disney Classic Games Collection - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Disney Classic Games Collection is the latest and greatest compilation of classic Disney games based on some of the most beloved Disney movies of all time: Aladdin, The Lion King, and now, The Jungle Book! Now you can play ALL of the critically acclaimed 16-Bit console versions of “Aladdin”, along with classic games based on Disney’s “The Jungle Book”! These all-new, fan requested, and beloved games complete this collection!

#DisneyClassicGames #NintendoSwitch
